70
00:09:14.912 --> 00:09:16.740
Abby off to school?

71
00:09:16.823 --> 00:09:20.167
Uh. not yet. She's. uh...
she's around here somewhere.

72
00:09:20.250 --> 00:09:21.969
Jeremiah's on his way over
to help me

73
00:09:22.052 --> 00:09:23.771
