-Okay. Bye.

83
00:09:45.108 --> 00:09:46.660
So. have you kissed her yet?

84
00:09:46.743 --> 00:09:48.338
No.

85
00:09:48.421 --> 00:09:49.831
Abs. it's not...
it's not like that.

86
00:09:49.914 --> 00:09:51.605
We're-we're just friends.

87
00:09:51.688 --> 00:09:54.335
