474
00:36:54.646 --> 00:36:56.257
Push it all away.

475
00:36:56.340 --> 00:36:57.676
<i>Faster.</i>

476
00:37:04.920 --> 00:37:06.223
<i>Faster.</i>

477
00:37:08.660 --> 00:37:09.919
