652
00:54:29.523 --> 00:54:30.742
Of course.

653
00:54:30.825 --> 00:54:32.179
Well. come on. We got to hurry.

654
00:54:32.262 --> 00:54:34.482
But first...

655
00:54:34.565 --> 00:54:37.157
