that will let me come with you.

658
00:54:54.990 --> 00:54:57.183
Will you enter it for me?

659
00:55:00.487 --> 00:55:01.924
Okay.

660
00:55:21.112 --> 00:55:22.529
N-No!

661
00:55:22.612 --> 00:55:24.028
-No!
-If you don't give me

662
