770
01:03:16.449 --> 01:03:18.042
Excuse me. Pardon me.

771
01:03:18.125 --> 01:03:19.570
-Look. it's Chica!
-Excuse me. Clear out.

772
01:03:19.653 --> 01:03:21.077
-Whoa.
-What's going on over here?

773
01:03:21.160 --> 01:03:23.722
Mr. Berg. this is my new
