to be sorry about.

785
01:03:59.227 --> 01:04:01.915
How about I go talk to him?

786
01:04:01.998 --> 01:04:03.381
What are you gonna say?

787
01:04:03.464 --> 01:04:05.589
I just want to see
what's going on

788
01:04:05.672 --> 01:04:08.309
